verbose_text: Overexpressing HOXC10-FL and HOXC10-F1 markedly promoted the luciferase activity of VEGFA, while overexpressing HOXC10-F2, HOXC10-F3, HOXC10-F4, all of which lacked the PRMT5 binding site or homeobox, could not activate the VEGFA promoter dependent luciferase activity.
